	<contentText >
		<text style="margin-bottom: 0;" ><![CDATA[Many people at work have been asking Emma how they can help Sandy.]]></text>
		<text style="margin-bottom: 0;" ><![CDATA[Emma approaches Sandy’s friend Dan, who works in Human Resources.]]></text>
	</contentText>
