		</strip>
		
		<strip id="2">
			<stripThumImg numberText="2" >
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Tumb_02.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" />
				<title><![CDATA[]]></title>
			</stripThumImg>
			<stripBackground>				
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Strip_02.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" ><![CDATA[]]></img>	
			</stripBackground>
			<stripCallOut align="top" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="550" y="140" width="280" arrowStyle="left: 20px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[Dan, I’m hoping you can help. I think Sandy’s family is having a hard time getting people to donate on Facebook, and when I visited Sandy yesterday she mentioned again how she will be out of work for a long time and is stressed about the medical costs.]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
		</strip>
		
		<strip id="3">
			<stripThumImg numberText="3" >	
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Tumb_03.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" />
				<title><![CDATA[]]></title>
			</stripThumImg>
			<stripBackground>				
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Strip_03.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" ><![CDATA[]]></img>		
			</stripBackground>
			<stripCallOut align="right" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="260" y="64" width="160" arrowStyle="top:15px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[I know. I feel terrible. It must be so scary for her.]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
			<stripCallOut align="left" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="637" y="20" width="100" arrowStyle="top:34px"/>
				<text ><![CDATA[I’m thinking the people who will be most willing to help are probably Sandy’s friends here at Johnson Controls. She knows so many people, and everyone likes her.]]></text>			
			</stripCallOut>
		</strip>
		
		<strip id="4">
			<stripThumImg numberText="4" >	
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Tumb_04.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" />
				<title><![CDATA[]]></title>
			</stripThumImg>
			<stripBackground>				
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Strip_04.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" ><![CDATA[]]></img>		
			</stripBackground>
			<stripCallOut align="right" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="260" y="64" width="160" arrowStyle="top:15px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[Yeah, hopefully everyone has seen the Facebook page.]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
		<stripCallOut align="top" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="550" y="140" width="280" arrowStyle="left: 20px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[It’s great, but a lot of people aren’t on Facebook, and the family has provided limited information. I figure my blog might be another way to reach people. I can share the fundraising information that I have and give some updates there.]]></text>			
			</stripCallOut>
		</strip>
		
		<strip id="5">
			<stripThumImg numberText="5" >	
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Tumb_05.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" />
				<title><![CDATA[]]></title>
			</stripThumImg>
			<stripBackground>				
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s13/Page_13_Strip_05.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" ><![CDATA[]]></img>		
			</stripBackground>
			<stripCallOut align="right" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="260" y="64" width="160" arrowStyle="top:15px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[That’s a good idea. What can I do to help?]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
			<stripCallOut align="top" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="550" y="140" width="280" arrowStyle="left: 20px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[Well, I know that I shouldn’t send out a company-wide email, but I was hoping maybe you could do that since it would be coming from HR? Maybe send a link to my blog and let people know what is going on with her medical situation.]]></text>			
			</stripCallOut>
		</strip>

